title: Marine Life Collection
description: An illustration featuring various marine organisms. At the top, there is a bird, likely a tern, holding a fish. Below it, a fish is depicted, followed by a long, slender fish. Next, there is a crab, and below that, a shrimp. Further down, there are illustrations of small marine creatures, possibly plankton, and green seaweed or algae at the bottom.

title: Wildlife Illustrations
description: The image features a collection of wildlife illustrations, including an otter, a duck, a heron, a muskrat, a grasshopper, various fish, a frog, and a snail. There are also circular illustrations depicting aquatic ecosystems, showcasing different species and their habitats.

title: Abstract Green Lines
description: An abstract design featuring several curved green lines that create a flowing, organic shape. The lines vary in thickness and direction, giving a sense of movement and fluidity.
